      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pad-alf-zzz-000.
           move      20                   to   w-pad-zzz-ctr          .
       pad-alf-zzz-100.
           if        w-pad-zzz-ctr        >    zero
                     if    w-pad-zzz-alf-chr
                          (w-pad-zzz-ctr) =    spaces
                           move    "z"    to   w-pad-zzz-alf-chr
                                              (w-pad-zzz-ctr)
