                           go to    pad-alf-zzz-100.
       pad-alf-zzz-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Trasformazione in uppercase                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       trf-des-upp-000.
           move      zero                 to   w-ctr                  .
       trf-des-upp-100.
           add       1                    to   w-ctr                  .
           if        w-ctr                >    40
                     go to  trf-des-upp-999.
           move      zero                 to   w-ulc                  .
           inspect   w-low            tallying w-ulc
                     for characters     before initial w-upp-chr
                                                      (w-ctr)         .
           if        w-ulc                <    26
                     add     1            to   w-ulc
                     move    w-upc(w-ulc) to   w-upp-chr(w-ctr)       .
           go to     trf-des-upp-100.
       trf-des-upp-999.
           exit.

